{"id": 2601, "date": "1988-07-07T11:00:59", "date_gmt": "1988-07-07T18:00:59", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=2601"}, "modified": "2026-02-22T11:28:22", "modified_gmt": "2026-02-22T19:28:22", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-jon-bon-jovi-its-my-life", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1988/07/07/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-jon-bon-jovi-its-my-life/", "title": {"rendered": "It&#8217;s My Life"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>A one-time-only performance: Jon Bon Jovi makes a guest appearance at Bruce&#8217;s 2003 holiday show in Asbury Park, and the two perform Bon Jovi&#8217;s &#8220;It&#8217;s My Life&#8221; together.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/a8A8IDk_Hd8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Bon Jovi&#8217;s original 2000 single peaked at #33 in the U.S., but it topped the charts in other countries and re-established the band for the new century.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vx2u5uUu3DE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></if